{"tid":1910284,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"NCT官方Twitter被駭客攻入","createTime":"2020-03-04T14:22:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T05:04:39.000Z","uid":170044,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3ff9dffa35541e557047f4b210f2884bbd191bd5","tid":1910284,"uid":170044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T14:22:38.000Z","msg":"時臨回歸之際，也算是誤打誤撞給回歸做了宣傳...<br />\n<br />\n今日（23日）上午，NCT 127的官方Twitter帳號被駭客團隊攻入，連發三條推文，除了下圖的兩條，還有一條寫的是「test」。這個駭客團隊的攻入表面是提醒帳戶安全，實際是為自己做廣告，除了NCT 127，許多著名人士或機構的帳戶也曾被他們攻入過。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">WFC?</span>"},{"pid":"fe0a6f909729a0606e702567e53ee858cb94a19b","tid":1910284,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T14:24:08.000Z","msg":"有人follow？"},{"pid":"7970eb34b91ad8b35c5bf293d0a794a75438bedb","tid":1910284,"uid":261796,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T14:24:50.000Z","msg":"NCT係咩嚟？"},{"pid":"d471d20a779eaeead50042f46bd908ae14593ddf","tid":1910284,"uid":170044,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe0a6f909729a0606e702567e53ee858cb94a19b","tid":1910284,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T14:24:08.000Z","msg":"有人follow？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T14:27:13.000Z","msg":"없습니다"},{"pid":"34f7e55315f4f4beace5f40d5657110727222103","tid":1910284,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d471d20a779eaeead50042f46bd908ae14593ddf","tid":1910284,"uid":170044,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe0a6f909729a0606e702567e53ee858cb94a19b","tid":1910284,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T14:24:08.000Z","msg":"有人follow？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T14:27:13.000Z","msg":"없습니다"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T14:27:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa